Privacy policy
This privacy policy applies between you, the User of this Website and Eveve Ltd, the owner and provider of this Website. Eveve Ltd takes the privacy of your information very seriously. This privacy policy applies to our use of any and all Data collected by us or provided by you in relation to your use of the Website.
Please read this privacy policy carefully
.
